复能量… 这样就显得我的人际交往总是不连续，总是浅尝辄止，总是中途放弃… 怎么办？这样的性格可以做需要大量人际交往的销售工作吗 (我有其他适合做销售的特质，但是人际交往这点让我非常自我怀疑)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-18a29b77b8daeba391ecc585bc95c205_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653433875"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+8bTi42psusnEAMaCTEwNzQ4NTM5MSChrIixBjAAOERADXIJNjUzNDMzODc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1713842355.918094", "card_id": "Q_652524773", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "从学校毕业之后还能如何提升自己的写作能力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c0402ebe0d431d29be397c40f65fe98c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652524773"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+8bTi42psusnEAMaCTEwNzI4Mjg5NiDDodqwBjAAOH5ADnIJNjUyNTI0NzczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1713842355.918623", "card_id": "Q_26036589", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 119}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么「女扮男装」比「男扮女装」要好看些？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这个问题应该是具有普遍性的，不排除极其看脸的特殊情况。事实上，一些被评长的比女人还漂亮的男人真扮起女人来，也总给一种不协调的感觉。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-40267ca0b4b23623aa804ad49b3ab435_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "n